cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for single-image depth perception. It also involves artificial intelligence (AI) methods for learning to estimate metric depth. Additionally, it could be categorized under computer graphics (GR) and robotics (RO) due to its potential applications in these fields.
